  "body": "Ensure we either have a PR or tracking issue (or mark as irrelevant) all features and changes in v1.2.0\r\n\r\nCurrently based on v1.2.0-rc.1 \r\n- [ ] Update this issue when v1.2.0 is released\r\n\r\n## Phase 0\r\n### Beacon chain\r\n\r\n- [ ] Add new DomainType for application usage with \"internal\" namespace https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/2884\r\n\r\n### Fork choice\r\n\r\n- [x] #4303\r\n  -  https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/2845\r\n- [x] [Bugfix]  Require fork choice to run before proposal https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/2878 https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/2897\r\n  - https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/4058\r\n- [x] Update PROPOSER_SCORE_BOOST to 40 percent https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/2895\r\n\r\n### Validator\r\n\r\n- [ ] Update 0x01 withdrawal credentials to balance update (no code exec) https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/2854\r\n\r\n### Networking\r\n\r\n- [x] Ignore subset aggregates https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/2847\r\n- [x] Ignore Aggregates Which Are Following the Wrong Finalized Checkpoint https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/2846\r\n- [ ] Deprecate BeaconBlocksByRange.step https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/2856\r\n\r\n## Altair\r\n### Light client\r\n- [ ] Ensure light client optimistic_header to be at head. [ref](https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/2814)\r\n- [ ] Consistently use compute_sync_committee_period. [ref](https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/2807)\r\n- [ ] Implement p2p interface [ref](https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/2802)\r\n\r\n## Bellatrix\r\n### Fork choice\r\n\r\n- [x] Add safe_block_hash and set to Justified https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/2851 https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/2858 https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/2876\r\n  -  https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/4080 \r\n- [x] Update PROPOSER_SCORE_BOOST to 40 percent https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/2895\r\n\r\n### Optimistic sync\r\n\r\n- [x] Optimistically import any post-merge block https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/2844\r\n- [x] Remove justified block from optimistic candidate conditions https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/2881\r\n  - PR: https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/4340 \r\n- [x] Remove INVALID_TERMINAL_BLOCK https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/2891\r\n  - PR : https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/4076\r\n- [ ] Remove API restrictions for optimistic sync https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/2869",
